ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

(@p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, @p32, @p33, @p34, 4),

(@p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, @p48, 6),
(@p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 7),
(@p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, @p61, @p62, 8),
(@p63, @p64, @p65, @p66, @p67, @p68, @p69, 9),
(@p70, @p71, @p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, 10),
(@p77, @p78, @p79, @p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, 11),
(@p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, @p88, @p89, @p90, 12)) AS i ([Author], [Content], [Link], [PublishDate], [SourceId], [Title], [Type], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Author], [Content], [Link], [PublishDate], [SourceId], [Title], [Type])
VALUES (i.[Author], i.[Content], i.[Link], i.[PublishDate], i.[SourceId], i.[Title], i.[Type])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Feeds] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];
